# Cloudflare Workers Static Assets redirects. Evaluated before the SPA
# not-found fallback, so these fire even though the old paths no longer have a
# static file. Query strings (?cat=&sub=) are preserved automatically.

# AI tools directory moved out of /learn → top-level /tools (2026-06-19).
# One splat rule covers the hub and all ~500 tool detail pages.
/learn/landscape          /tools/            301
/learn/landscape/*        /tools/:splat      301
